{"problem":{"stackLimit":128,"modifiedUser":"root","auth":1,"isRemote":false,"description":"<p>在一个旧式的火车站旁边有一座桥，其桥面可以绕河中心的桥墩水平旋转。一个车站的职工发现桥的长度最多能容纳两节车厢，如果将桥旋转180度，则可以把相邻两节车厢的位置交换，用这种方法可以重新排列车厢的顺序。于是他就负责用这座桥将进站的车厢按车厢号从小到大排列。他退休后，火车站决定将这一工作自动化，其中一项重要的工作是编一个程序，输入初始的车厢顺序，计算最少用多少步就能将车厢排序。<p>","removeEndBlank":true,"uploadCase":true,"source":"","remote":false,"title":"车厢重组 ","type":0,"difficulty":1,"output":"<p>一个数据，是最少的旋转次数。<p>","timeLimit":1000,"input":"<p>有两行数据，第一行是车厢总数N（不大于10000），第二行是N个不同的数表示初始的车厢顺序。<p>","examples":"<input>4\n4 3 2 1\n\n</input><output>6\n</output>","ioScore":10000,"codeShare":false,"hint":"","isRemoveEndBlank":true,"openCaseResult":true,"memoryLimit":256,"problemId":"T1310","isUploadCase":true},"languages":["C","C With O2","C++","C++ With O2","Java","Python3","Python2","Golang","C#"],"codeTemplates":[],"isSpj":false,"samples":[{"output":"1.out","input":"1.in","score":100},{"output":"2.out","input":"2.in","score":100},{"output":"3.out","input":"3.in","score":100},{"output":"4.out","input":"4.in","score":100},{"output":"5.out","input":"5.in","score":100},{"output":"6.out","input":"6.in","score":100},{"output":"7.out","input":"7.in","score":100},{"output":"8.out","input":"8.in","score":100},{"output":"9.out","input":"9.in","score":100},{"output":"10.out","input":"10.in","score":100}],"tags":["一本通在线评测"]}